Quick Installation Guide
------------------------

(1) Review mrhttpd.conf
(2) ./configure
(3) make
(4) as root: make install

NB: you can skip step 2 and 3 if you feel lucky


Public Docker Image
-------------------

docker run -d -p 8080:8080 -v <local directory>:/opt/mrhttpd/public dockahdockah/mrhttpd
